2401BDF345A: 00 00                 - add [rax],al
2401BDF345C: 00 00                 - add [rax],al
2401BDF345E: 00 00                 - add [rax],al
// ---------- INJECTING HERE ----------
PlayerCharacter:AddMoney: 55                    - push rbp
